abstract: Professor FitzGibbon served as a co-organizer for the Symposium on the Jurisprudence of Family Relations: Privacy, Autonomy, and Should States Regulate Family Relations? at the Cardozo Law School of Yeshiva University.
title: Co-Organizer: Symposium on the Jurisprudence of Family Relations: Privacy, Autonomy, and Should States Regulate Family Relations?
subject: law
